DIFFRACTION
OF
A
PLANE
WAVE
BY
A
UNIDIRECTIONALLY
CONDUCTING
HALF
PLANE
THE
PROBLEM
IS
FORMULATED
IN
TERMS
OF
AN
INTEGRAL
EQUATION
SPECIFYING
THE
SCREEN
FUNCTION
WHOSE
SOLUTION
IS
OBTAINED
BY
THE
STANDARD
WIENER
HOPF
PROCEDURE
EXPRESSIONS
FOR
THE
FIELDS
AND
THE
CURRENT
INDUCED
ON
THE
HALF
PLANE
ARE
GIVEN
